title: Ziad Rahbani - Live at Damascus Citadel 2008
description:
Ziad Rahbani (also Ziyad al-Rahbany, born 1956) is a Lebanese composer, pianist, performer, playwright, and political commentator. His compositions are well known throughout the Arab world. Many of his musicals satirize Lebanese politics both during and after the civil war, and are often strongly critical of the traditional political establishment.
